race.comment: Very competitive highweight with little between the top half dozen. FLOOD AND FIRE (4) was over the hurdles last time in but has more than enough flat ability for this. Good run fresh with a big weight and strips fitter for the extra ground. Looks a good improver. SANIKA (7) has been racing well and is overdue for a win. Course and distance winner and overdue. Expected to feature. COSMIC (9) is another racing well including a two-length maiden win two back. Form is good for this and will be winding up late.  LITTLEBITCHEEKY (8) disappointed last time at Colac when 6 lengths from the winner in sixth. Was a winner the start prior and In the mix on best form. Tricky draw but expected to give a sight.
